{"tid":1364711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺隊波，係咪由元朗鄉紳組成？","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T12:23:34.000Z","uid":260104,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7d438ccce14c6f2b53e5afaf86ac5095a58abc","tid":1364711,"uid":260104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"成隊波黎打人既，都唔係踢波。<br />\n<br />\n都係我地阿記係清泉，好似香港人咁，過往成績彪炳，但依家比人迫害。同雲爺爺一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同意既請正評，然後上一頁，繼續推727<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365a5a3e5e71eb4fadfe6d5df5c399ce9c20ebc1","tid":1364711,"uid":35348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"都係著白衫"},{"pid":"a95cd27d8cd774b7ab155834560d7d2391de4f1f","tid":1364711,"uid":260104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365a5a3e5e71eb4fadfe6d5df5c399ce9c20ebc1","tid":1364711,"uid":35348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"都係著白衫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"係wow，，，班牛屎佬去晒打曼狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5abf4ee90f2508bea4f95086e8200b98e650114","tid":1364711,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d1998b9c4a17ed53c816707fec679aa63bc5a200","tid":1364711,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6ZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=bee16f15\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"218981e28bbbaa0473df840f6c1a7dcf9b75